Presidential Libraries

     GENERAL INFORMATION
     * An Overview of the Presidential Libraries system may answer some of
       your general questions about the Presidential Library program.
     * Application and Permit for Use of Space in Presidential Libraries
       and Grounds
     * Library Research Room Hours: Monday - Friday, 9 am - 5 pm (closed
       all federal holidays).
     * Museum Hours: Presidential Library museums are open every day
       except Thanksgiving, Christmas and New Year's Day (the Johnson
       Library is only closed Christmas Day).
       See below for individual museum hours.
     * Directions: Please refer to the individual library's webpage.
     * Grants are available to assist researchers studying Presidential
       Libraries holdings.

     [Up] GEORGE BUSH LIBRARY
     http://bushlibrary.tamu.edu
     1000 George Bush Drive West
     College Station, TX 77845
     PHONE: 979-260-9554
     FAX: 979-260-9557
     EMAIL: bush.library@nara.gov

     Museum Hours:
     9:30 am - 5 pm, Monday - Saturday
     12 pm - 5 pm, Sunday
     Museum Admission: $5.00
     (students 17+ $4, sr. citizens 62+ $3.50, children under 16 free)

